        <h1>Remedies for Hair Fall</h1>
        <h2>Egg Mask</h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>Rich in protien, sulphur, zinc, and phosphorus, eggs make a fantastic remedy to treat persistent hair fall.
            Eggs strengthen hair strands, promotes hair growth, and prevents split ends.</p>
        <p>To prepare the egg mask:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Separate one egg white in a bowl and add a teaspoon each of olive oil and honey.</li>
            <li>Beat to make a paste and apply it all over from root to tips.</li>
            <li>After 20 minutes, rinse with a mild shampoo.</li>
            <li>Apply this mask once a week.</li>
        </ol>
            </div>
