        <h2>Aloe Vera</h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>Aloe Vera is an effective home remedy for hair loss and to boost hair growth. It is also effective in reducing problems 
            of the scalp like itching and flaking.</p>
        <p>To prepare the aloe vera mask:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Take the stalk of Aloe Vera and extract the pulp.</li>
            <li>Apply it to your hair and scalp and leave it for about 45 minutes.</li>
            <li>Rinse with normal water. You can do this three to four times a week to see better results.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
